atening people for having seeds blown in to their fields.<br /><br />&quot;Organic&quot; farmers are thriving in an uneducated market where consumers neither understand or want to know how their foods get made. That said, it's pretty undesirable to see Monsanto's monoculture in crops.

              

              
              
