            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              CRmarvin42 wrote &quot;No one has ever died or even gotten sick from GMO because of the changed gene.&quot;<br />This would be a very difficult claim to prove.<br />In the early years of the last century radium was the hot thing (no pun intended). It was highly touted for a variety of things, sold by trained Physicians etc. That did not turn out so well as a multitude of people died because of something they were promoting that they did not understand. It was however the best science of the day. GMO's are PROBABLY safe but before we dedicate our ENTIRE ecosystem to them I want more safety studies done. Biologic systems are incredibly complex. The caveat of Murphy's law and unintended consequences come to mind.

              

              
              
            </div>
